OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRail workers given fresh   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay offer in dispute       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rail workers have been given a fresh   
OL,6, pay offer by train companies in a bid  
OL,7, to end long-running strike action.     
OL,9,FThe Rail Delivery Group (RDG) has made 
OL,10,Fthe new offer to the RMT union         
OL,11,Ffollowing talks over the past week.    
OL,13,FThe deal includes a backdated pay rise 
OL,14,Fof 5%, up from a previous offer of 4%  
OL,15,Ffor 2022, and a 4% increase this year. 
OL,16,FBut the deal depends on changes to     
OL,17,Fworking conditions.                    
OL,19,FThe RMT said it was "considering" the  
OL,20,Fmatter.                                
